| Task                     | Primary reference              |
|--------------------------|--------------------------------|
| RPC list / behavior      | `docs/context/RPC_CATALOG.md`  |
| Storage / schema         | `docs/context/STORAGE_CATALOG.md`, `MIGRATIONS.md` |
| Security / limits        | `docs/context/SECURITY_MODEL.md` |
| Caching / performance    | `docs/context/PERFORMANCE_PLAYBOOK.md` |
| Logging / metrics        | `docs/context/OBSERVABILITY.md` |
| What to build next       | `docs/context/EXECUTION_PLAN.md` |
| High-level architecture  | `docs/context/ARCHITECTURE.md`  |
